<section id="nanban" class="nanban-section">
  <div class="nanban-content">
    <h2 class="nanban-title">About Nanban</h2>
    <p class="nanban-description">
      Nanban is more than just an assistive device – it’s a companion designed to empower visually impaired individuals with smart assistance in everyday life. By combining cutting-edge technology like object detection, distance measurement, and voice assistance, Nanban creates a safer, more independent world for its users.
    </p>
    <p class="nanban-description">
      Nanban is designed to help users with:
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Environmental Awareness</strong>: Detect and identify objects around you, providing real-time distance and position data to ensure safe navigation.</li>
        <li><strong>Voice Assistance</strong>: Respond to voice commands to get information such as the current time, weather, news, and even listen to YouTube audio.</li>
        <li><strong>Enhanced Mobility</strong>: With clear auditory feedback, Nanban allows users to navigate their surroundings with more confidence and control.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p class="nanban-description">
      Whether you are at home, in public spaces, or simply moving around, Nanban is your personal assistant, offering real-time support to help you make informed decisions, stay safe, and engage with the world around you.
    </p>
    <p class="nanban-description">
      Nanban’s simple interface allows for effortless interaction, while its adaptability ensures that it grows with your needs, providing a continuously evolving support system.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="#store" class="cta-button get-started">Get Started</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
